description:
Kate and Doree help a listener pick out the best skincare product to give a cherished friend on her 40th birthday. Then the women offer non-app dating tips and answer an email from a listener dealing with a stressful semester abroad. Plus, they discuss the ultimate form of self-care: washing your butt in a bidet.
